man im in a state of crisis with my decks
Taniwha — really happy with right now! made some recent changes and it played really well last night. It’s basically stax / extra turns / free counterspells / mana rocks

5c enchantress — i decided to try to make my deck better from marath by going 5c but really all i did was turn the deck into something that races for the omniscience combo and it’s super inconsistent. Needs to get torn up. I want to have an enchantress deck still but not sure what i want to do.

Sidisi UV Control — this deck use to be better in my meta 2 years ago. i finally went back to UV it after a bunch of trying out different mono black commanders. i just cant get it to work anymore. i need my decks to be more proactive these days. My choices are either do something not as tryhard in mono black that’s more fun, or maybe add some colors to the control shell (tasigur?)
Adun Oakenshield — no salvaging this one, im just too lazy to take it apart
Etali, new dinosaur — this deck is not good IMO. it has splashy plays but it never actually wins.

so why i’m posting here, i need ideas!

 - i need something to put all my baller black & red cards in
